---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
---

<section id="open-source" class="pb-64 text-center pt-28 bg-pine-50">
  <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto">
    <h2
      class="relative z-10 inline text-4xl font-bold font-display after:bg-pine-100 after:-z-10 text-pine-800 after:w-full after:h-1/2 after:absolute after:left-0 after:-bottom-1 after:rounded-full"
    >
      Free and open-source
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-10 text-xl">
      We absolutely love open-source!<br />
      Castopod is licensed under
      <a
        href="https://code.castopod.org/adaures/castopod/-/blob/develop/LICENSE.md"
        class="font-semibold hover:underline decoration-pine-500 decoration-2"
        >AGPL v3</a
      >, it is open <em>to everyone</em>, <em>in every sense</em>, and meant to
      stay this way.
    </p>

    <div class="flex items-center justify-center mt-8 gap-x-2">
      <a
        href="https://code.castopod.org/adaures/castopod"
        class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 font-semibold text-white border-2 border-transparent rounded-full shadow-md group gap-x-2 bg-pine-500 hover:bg-pine-800 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-pine-400 focus:ring-opacity-75"
      >
        <Icon
          pack="ri"
          name="gitlab-fill"
          class="h-6 text-pine-800 group-hover:text-pine-500"
        />Source code
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/ad-aures/castopod"
        class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 font-semibold border-2 rounded-full border-pine-500 text-pine-500 gap-x-2 bg-pine-50 hover:bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-pine-400 focus:ring-opacity-75"
      >
        <Icon pack="ri" name="github-fill" class="h-6" />Github
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
